data.description: 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home in the Tranquil Setting of Imperial Harbor, Bonita Springs. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and community in this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled within Imperial Harbour of Bonita Springs. Built in 2004, this residence offers a spacious living area that invites you to unwind and create cherished memories with loved ones. The thoughtful layout features split bedrooms, providing an added layer of privacy for residents and guests alike. Whether it's family gatherings or quiet evenings, this home's design caters to your every need. Recent updates include a fresh interior paint job, breathing new life into the space and providing a blank canvas for your personal touch making this home move-in ready. Located within the exclusive 55+ community of Imperial Harbour, this residence offers more than just a home; it offers a lifestyle. Immerse yourself in the vibrant social scene, where neighbors become friends and shared activities create lasting bonds. The community's amenities cater to a variety of interests, ensuring there's always something exciting to do. Bonita Springs is renowned for its tranquil ambiance, yet it's just a short drive from bustling urban centers, ensuring you have the best of both worlds. With nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment options, you'll never be far from the necessities and luxuries of life.
